The candidate of the Peoples Democratic Party, in Kogi State, Wada Musa has won Yagba East in the November 16th gubernatorial election. Musa scored over 7,000 votes against the 6,735 votes recorded by the candidate of the All Progressives Congress, Yahaya Bello. Yahaya Bello is the incumbent Governor. READ LATEST UPDATES HERE See the result: Yagba East
